        What the Body Corporate Manager Does: a Brisbane Unit Seller's Guide
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Most unit sellers underestimate how much the body corporate manager affects their sale. Here is what the BCM does, what they must provide you, and the questions to ask before you list.
      </p>
